quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,Haa Meem
  44,2,Kasam hai is kitaab e Mubeen ki
  44,3,"Ke humne isey ek badi khair o barakat wali raat mein nazil kiya hai, kyunke hum logon ko mutanabbeh (warning) karne ka irada rakhte thay"
  44,4,Yeh woh raat thi jismein har maamle ka hakeemana faisla
  44,5,Hamare hukum se sadir kiya jata hai. Hum ek Rasool bhejne waley thay
  44,6,Tere Rubb ki rehmat ke taur par.Yaqeenan wahi sab kuch sunne aur jaanne wala hai
  44,7,Aasmano aur zameen ka Rubb aur har us cheez ka Rubb jo Aasman o zameen ke darmiyan hai agar tum log waqaii yakeen rakhne waley ho
  44,8,Koi maabood uske siwa nahin hai. Wahi zindagi ata karta hai aur wahi maut deta hai.Tumhara Rubb aur tumhare un aslaaf (forefathers) ka Rubb jo pehle guzar chuke hain
  44,9,(Magar fil-waqeh in logon ko yaqeen nahin hai) balke yeh apne shakk mein paday khel rahey hain
  44,10,Accha intezar karo us din ka jab aasman sareeh dhuwan (smoke) liye huey aayega
  44,11,"Aur woh logon par chaa jayega, yeh hai dardnaak saza"
  44,12,"(Ab kehte hain ke) “ parwardigar , humpar se yeh azaab taal de, hum imaan laatey hain”"
  44,13,Inki gaflat kahan dur hoti hai? Inka haal to yeh hai ke in ke paas Rasool e mubeen aa gaya
  44,14,Phir bhi yeh uski taraf multafit na huey aur kaha ke “ yeh to sikhaya padaya bawla hai (well-tutored madman)”
  44,15,"Hum zara azaab hataye detay hain, tum log phir wahi kuch karoge jo pehle kar rahe thay"
  44,16,Jis roz hum badi zarb (assault) lagayenge woh din hoga jab hum tumse intiqaam lenge
  44,17,Hum insey pehle Firaun ki qaum ko isi aazmaish mein daal chuke hain. Unke paas ek nihayat shareef Rasool aaya
  44,18,"Aur usne kaha “Allah ke bandon ko mere hawale karo, main tumhare liye ek amanat-daar Rasool hoon"
  44,19,Allah ke muqable mein sarkashi na karo. Main tumhare saamne (apni maamuriyat ki) sareeh sanad (clear authority) pesh karta hoon
  44,20,Aur main apne Rubb aur tumhare Rubb ki panaah le chuka hoon issey ke tum mujhpar hamla-awar (attack) ho
  44,21,Agar tum meri baat nahin maante to mujhpar haath daalne se baaz raho”
  44,22,Aakhir e kaar usne apne Rubb ko pukara ke yeh log mujrim hain
  44,23,(Jawab diya gaya) accha to raat-o-raat mere bandon (servants) ko lekar chal padh. Tum logon ka peecha kiya jayega
  44,24,Samandar ko uske haal par khula chodh de.Yeh saara lashkar garq (drown) honay wala hai
  44,25,Kitne hi baag aur chasme
  44,26,Aur kheit (gardens) aur shaandaar mahal thay jo woh chodh gaye
  44,27,"Kitne hi aish ke sar-o-samaan, jin mein woh mazey kar rahey thay unke pichey dharay reh gaye"
  44,28,"Yeh hua unka anjaam, aur humne dusron ko in cheezon ka waris bana diya"
  44,29,"Phir na aasman unpar roya na zameen, aur zara si mohalat bhi unko na di gayi"